Hi,

I am currently using the SDS MK4i Modules and 364’s BaseFalconSwerve. I am facing a problem in which we can drive forwards but cannot rotate. But if we change the offsets, we are able to rotate but not drive in the direction we consider forwards. We have another branch that does work but when we copy and paste it into master, It no longer works and we have the same problem stated above.
